### 链表式指标点测试

### 1. 构建链表结构
POST localhost:8080/api/collegeadmin/indicator-points/build-linked-list?majorCategoryId=1422192039766843392
token: {{token}}

### 2. 获取链表根节点
GET localhost:8080/api/collegeadmin/indicator-points/linked-list/root?majorCategoryId=1422192039766843392
token: {{token}}

> {%
    client.global.set("root_node_id", response.body.data[0].id);
%}

### 3. 获取第一个子节点
GET localhost:8080/api/collegeadmin/indicator-points/linked-list/{{root_node_id}}/first-child
token: {{token}}

> {%
    client.global.set("first_child_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### 4. 获取下一个兄弟节点
GET localhost:8080/api/collegeadmin/indicator-points/linked-list/{{first_child_id}}/next-sibling
token: {{token}}

### 5. 获取所有直接子节点（替代方案）
GET localhost:8080/api/collegeadmin/indicator-points/linked-list/{{root_node_id}}/children
token: {{token}}